{"arkId":"cl010099888","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010099888","modified ":"2026-03-11","title":"Statuette \u00e9questre de Charlemagne ou de Charles le Chauve","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Statuette \u00e9questre de Charlemagne ou de Charles le Chauve"},{"type":"Ancien titre","value":"Statuette \u00e9questre : \u0022Charlemagne\u0022 ou Charles le Chauve"},{"type":"Autre titre","value":"Statuette de Charlemagne"},{"type":"Autre titre","value":"Statuette dite de Charlemagne"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Charlemagne (771-814) (Occident-\u003Emoyen \u00e2ge-\u003Ehaut moyen \u00e2ge-\u003Edynastie des Carolingiens (752-987)) (?) ; Charles II le Chauve (843-877) (Occident-\u003Emoyen \u00e2ge-\u003Ehaut moyen \u00e2ge-\u003Edynastie des Carolingiens (752-987)) (?) ; Antiquit\u00e9 tardive (Antiquit\u00e9-\u003E\u00e9poque romaine) (?) ; Epoque imp\u00e9riale romaine (Antiquit\u00e9-\u003E\u00e9poque romaine) (?)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 200 - 500 (datation du cheval possible du Haut-Empire ou du Bas-Empire) et 800 - 900 (cavalier) et 1700 - 1800 (cheval restaur\u00e9)","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 501 - Charlemagne, Vitrine 3 pat\u00e8ne de Saint-Denis","room":"Salle 501, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":200,"endYear":500,"imprecision":"","text":"IIIe si\u00e8cle (?) ; Ve si\u00e8cle (?)","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""},{"startYear":800,"endYear":900,"imprecision":"","text":"IXe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""},{"startYear":1700,"endYear":1800,"imprecision":"","text":"XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Anonyme","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q4233718"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 8260","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"statuette \u00e9questre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"La statuette dite \u0022de Charlemagne\u0022 fut retrouv\u00e9e par Alexandre Lenoir en 1807 ; elle appartenait au tr\u00e9sor de la cath\u00e9drale de Metz. Ce bronze s\u0027inspire de statues \u00e9questres antiques comme celle de Marc Aur\u00e8le \u00e0 Rome. La figuration de Charlemagne ou de Charles le Chauve sous les traits du cavalier souligne l\u0027int\u00e9r\u00eat des souverains carolingiens pour le r\u00e9pertoire antique. L\u0027empereur, tenant un globe (orbe) et une \u00e9p\u00e9e (aujourd\u0027hui disparue), s\u0027affirme comme un conqu\u00e9rant, un \u0022nouveau C\u00e9sar\u0022 aux yeux du monde.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"24","displayDimension":"24 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"19,5","displayDimension":"19,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"17,5","displayDimension":"17,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"9,5","displayDimension":"9,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau\/Technique : Bronze avec traces de dorure\r\nMat\u00e9riau : bronze\r\nTechnique : fonte = coul\u00e9 fondu = fondu (techniques m\u00e9tal)","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"cath\u00e9drale (Moselle-\u003EMetz) (tr\u00e9sor de la cath\u00e9drale)","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Tr\u00e9sor de la cath\u00e9drale de Metz ; acquise en 1807 chez un libraire \u00e0 Metz par Alexandre Lenoir (1761-1839) ; vente Lenoir \u00e0 Paris, 11-16 d\u00e9cembre 1837, n\u00b0 121 ; acquis par M. Evans-Lombe (1850 ?) pour la somme de 1000 francs ; Mme Evans-Lombe, vente Evans-Lombe \u00e0 Paris, 27 avril 1863, n\u00b0 78 ; acquise par la Ville de Paris pour la somme de 5000 francs avant 1871 et conserv\u00e9e \u00e0 H\u00f4tel de Ville en attente du futur mus\u00e9e historique de Paris puis, apr\u00e8s l\u0027incendie de l\u0027H\u00f4tel de Ville en 1871, confi\u00e9e au mus\u00e9e Carnavalet ; d\u00e9p\u00f4t-\u00e9change avec le mus\u00e9e du Louvre, arr\u00eat\u00e9 du 3 ao\u00fbt 1934.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Ville de Paris","note":"","role":", Institution \/ Mus\u00e9e"},{"value":"Evans-Lombe","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"},{"value":"Lenoir, Alexandre","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"d\u00e9p\u00f4t","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"26\/07\/1934","startYear":1934,"endYear":1934},{"type":"date de l\u0027arr\u00eat\u00e9\/d\u00e9cision","value":"03\/08\/1934","startYear":1934,"endYear":1934},{"type":"date du conseil","value":"13\/11\/1934","startYear":1934,"endYear":1934}]}],"ownedBy":"Mus\u00e9e Carnavalet, Paris","heldBy":"","longTermLoanTo":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"d\u00e9p\u00f4t"}],"period":[{"value":"Charlemagne (771-814)"},{"value":"Charles II le Chauve (843-877)"},{"value":"Antiquit\u00e9 tardive"},{"value":"Epoque imp\u00e9riale romaine"}],"place":[{"value":"cath\u00e9drale"}],"objectType":[{"value":"statuette \u00e9questre"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Fonkenell, Guillaume (dir.), A cheval : le portrait \u00e9questre dans la France de la Renaissance, cat. exp. (Ecouen (Externe, France), Mus\u00e9e de la Renaissance - ch\u00e2teau d\u